      "title": "Background",
      "text": "'Even if death is the predetermined end… please don't walk that final path alone.'\n\nA family curse. The burden of tending the dead for the Burial Society. The coffin that she carries wherever she goes. No matter how one sees this former Vice-Commander of Bell Ringer Saint Albrecht, death is never far from her side.\n\nAnd that solemn duty—bound so closely to death—now quietly knocks upon the door of Piera's fate.",
